  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Hermit Drying Rack</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Hermit Drying Rack</b> is a naturally spawning object exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them\" title=\"Return of Them\">Return of Them</a></i>. Six of them can be found on the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Island\" title=\"Hermit Island\">Hermit Island</a>.\n</p><p>The Hermit Drying Rack works just like a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Drying_Rack/DST\" title=\"Drying Rack/DST\">Drying Rack</a>, except that it cannot be destroyed or burned and can only dry one item at a time.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Dryable_Items\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dryable Items</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Skins\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Skins</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Assets\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Assets</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dryable_Items\">Dryable Items</span></h2>\n<p>The list of possible Food that can be dried:\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Item\n</th>\n<th>Dried\n</th>\n<th>Time required\n</th>\n<th>Spoil Timer\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Meat.png/32px-Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Jerky\" title=\"Jerky\"><img alt=\"Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Jerky.png/32px-Jerky.png?41c73e\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>2 days\n</td>\n<td>20 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Monster_Meat.png/32px-Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Jerky\" title=\"Monster Jerky\"><img alt=\"Monster Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Monster_Jerky.png/32px-Monster_Jerky.png?46a27a\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>20 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Raw_Fish\" title=\"Raw Fish\"><img alt=\"Raw Fish.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Raw_Fish.png/32px-Raw_Fish.png?c251a7\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishy_Jerky\" title=\"Fishy Jerky\"><img alt=\"Fishy Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fishy_Jerky.png/32px-Fishy_Jerky.png?26ec91\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>15 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Batilisk_Wing\" title=\"Batilisk Wing\"><img alt=\"Batilisk Wing.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Batilisk_Wing.png/32px-Batilisk_Wing.png?5f6c51\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Naked_Nostrils\" title=\"Naked Nostrils\"><img alt=\"Naked Nostrils.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Naked_Nostrils.png/32px-Naked_Nostrils.png?f797e5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Small_Jerky\" title=\"Small Jerky\"><img alt=\"Small Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Small_Jerky.png/32px-Small_Jerky.png?23f97d\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>2 days\n</td>\n<td>20 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morsel\" title=\"Morsel\"><img alt=\"Morsel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Morsel.png/32px-Morsel.png?fe6bb2\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Legs\" title=\"Frog Legs\"><img alt=\"Frog Legs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Frog_Legs.png/32px-Frog_Legs.png?523667\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Drumstick\" title=\"Drumstick\"><img alt=\"Drumstick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Drumstick.png/32px-Drumstick.png?87012f\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>20 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Morsel\" title=\"Fish Morsel\"><img alt=\"Fish Morsel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fish_Morsel.png/32px-Fish_Morsel.png?ec4421\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Small_Fishy_Jerky\" title=\"Small Fishy Jerky\"><img alt=\"Small Fishy Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Small_Fishy_Jerky.png/32px-Small_Fishy_Jerky.png?4c4c9f\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>0.5 day\n</td>\n<td>15 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eel\" title=\"Eel\"><img alt=\"Eel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Eel.png/32px-Eel.png?ea28c8\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>15 days\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Petals\" title=\"Petals\"><img alt=\"Petals.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Petals.png/32px-Petals.png?d5ab74\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Petals\" title=\"Dried Petals\"><img alt=\"Dried Petals.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Petals.png/32px-Dried_Petals.png?38c13c\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dark_Petals\" title=\"Dark Petals\"><img alt=\"Dark Petals.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dark_Petals.png/32px-Dark_Petals.png?404a29\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Dark_Petals\" title=\"Dried Dark Petals\"><img alt=\"Dried Dark Petals.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Dark_Petals.png/32px-Dried_Dark_Petals.png?3daebe\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Foliage.png/32px-Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Foliage\" title=\"Dried Foliage\"><img alt=\"Dried Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Foliage.png/32px-Dried_Foliage.png?db113c\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Succulent\" title=\"Succulent\"><img alt=\"Succulent.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Succulent.png/32px-Succulent.png?8db2ed\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Succulent\" title=\"Dried Succulent\"><img alt=\"Dried Succulent.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Succulent.png/32px-Dried_Succulent.png?c20bb0\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lune_Tree_Blossom\" title=\"Lune Tree Blossom\"><img alt=\"Lune Tree Blossom.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lune_Tree_Blossom.png/32px-Lune_Tree_Blossom.png?63eb45\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Lune_Tree_Blossom\" title=\"Dried Lune Tree Blossom\"><img alt=\"Dried Lune Tree Blossom.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Lune_Tree_Blossom.png/32px-Dried_Lune_Tree_Blossom.png?6b7210\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Nettle_Fronds\" title=\"Fire Nettle Fronds\"><img alt=\"Fire Nettle Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fire_Nettle_Fronds.png/32px-Fire_Nettle_Fronds.png?e0cdb0\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Fire_Nettle_Frond\" title=\"Dried Fire Nettle Frond\"><img alt=\"Dried Fire Nettle Frond.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Fire_Nettle_Frond.png/32px-Dried_Fire_Nettle_Frond.png?417f9e\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tillweeds\" title=\"Tillweeds\"><img alt=\"Tillweeds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Tillweeds.png/32px-Tillweeds.png?d5e0cb\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Tillweed\" title=\"Dried Tillweed\"><img alt=\"Dried Tillweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Tillweed.png/32px-Dried_Tillweed.png?bee357\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Forget-Me-Lots.png/32px-Forget-Me-Lots.png?be6524\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots.png/32px-Dried_Forget-Me-Lots.png?332337\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>1 day\n</td>\n<td>x\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Kelp_Fronds.png/32px-Kelp_Fronds.png?cb9519\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Dried Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Dried Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dried_Kelp_Fronds.png/32px-Dried_Kelp_Fronds.png?502d38\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a></td>\n<td>0.25 days\n</td>\n<td>20 days\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Skins\"><img alt=\"Voidbag Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Voidbag_Icon.png/32px-Voidbag_Icon.png?3b640b\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\"> Skins</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"box headnote\"><i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Glommer%27s_Flower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glommer&#x27;s Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Glommer%27s_Flower.png/25px-Glommer%27s_Flower.png?22167d\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\"></a> Main article:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Belongings#Natural_Object_Skins\" title=\"Belongings\">Belongings</a></span><br>\n</p>\n<ul><li>The <b><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\">Event</span></b> skin does not drop normally. Instead, it is usable by everyone during the official <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\">Winter&#x27;s Feast</a> event.</li></ul>\n<div>  \n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Coral_Meat_Rack_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Coral Meat Rack Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Coral_Meat_Rack_Icon.png/107px-Coral_Meat_Rack_Icon.png?e29e8a\" width=\"107\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-elegant\"><b>Woven - Elegant</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-collection\"><b>Shelled Collection</b></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Coral Meat Rack</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>Add a deliciously fishy kick to your jerky!</i></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hermit Drying Rack Merrymaker.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png/107px-Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png?a54205\" width=\"107\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\"><b>Event</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-collection\"><b>The Merrymaker Collection</b></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>n/a</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>n/a</i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"> Assets</span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Hermit_Drying_Rack-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Hermit_Drying_Rack-0\">Hermit Drying Rack</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"The_Merrymaker-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#The_Merrymaker-0\">The Merrymaker</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Coral_Meat_Rack-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Drying_Rack#Coral_Meat_Rack-0\">Coral Meat Rack</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Build\"><img alt=\"Build\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack.png/103px-Hermit_Drying_Rack.png?e83833\" width=\"103\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Build</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack_Idle.gif\" class=\"image\" title=\"Idle\"><img alt=\"Idle\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack_Idle.gif/105px-Hermit_Drying_Rack_Idle.gif?307a11\" width=\"105\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Idle</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack_Burnt.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Burnt (Unused)\"><img alt=\"Burnt (Unused)\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack_Burnt.png/101px-Hermit_Drying_Rack_Burnt.png?c26c2f\" width=\"101\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Burnt (Unused)</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Build\"><img alt=\"Build\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png/107px-Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png?a54205\" width=\"107\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Build</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker_Idle.gif\" class=\"image\" title=\"Idle\"><img alt=\"Idle\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker_Idle.gif/107px-Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker_Idle.gif?be11e0\" width=\"107\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Idle</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Coral_Meat_Rack_Build.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Build\"><img alt=\"Build\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Coral_Meat_Rack_Build.png/104px-Coral_Meat_Rack_Build.png?3e8343\" width=\"104\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Build</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Coral_Meat_Rack_Idle.gif\" class=\"image\" title=\"Idle\"><img alt=\"Idle\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Coral_Meat_Rack_Idle.gif/104px-Coral_Meat_Rack_Idle.gif?af4878\" width=\"104\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Idle</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/