  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Giá phơi đồ Hermit là một vật thể sinh sản tự nhiên độc quyền trong Don&#x27;t Starve Together, được giới thiệu trong Return of Them. Sáu trong số chúng có thể được tìm thấy trên Đảo Hermit.</p>",
  "title": "Hermit Drying Rack",
  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|perk = Dry [[Food]] items.\n|spawnCode = \"meatrack_hermit\"\n|image =  Hermit Drying Rack.png\n}}\n{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Those look like they could use some meat.\n|willow = Maybe I'll leave some meat here before I leave...\n|wolfgang = Is sad and meat-less.\n|wendy = One can't survive long without food...\n|wx78 = AS IF I WOULD HELP THAT OLD MEATSACK...\n|wickerbottom = It seems our chitinous friend could use some assistance.\n|woodie = Whatcha think, Lucy? Do we have some meat to spare?\n|maxwell = Perhaps if she were fed, she'd be less ill-tempered.\n|wigfrid = I'd be cantankeröus töö if I were left withöut meat!\n|webber = Maybe we could share some meat?\n|winona = Maybe I should give the old lady a hand.\n|warly = It looks so bare... perhaps I could put some meat on it.\n|wortox = Her hooks are bare, but should I care?\n|wormwood = Need food?\n|wurt = These belong to crabby lady, florp.\n|walter = Those are some pretty swell looking drying racks.\n|wanda = Maybe I could help the poor old thing, if I have a spare minute or two...\n|choose = wurt}}\nThe '''Hermit Drying Rack''' is a naturally spawning object exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', introduced in ''[[Return of Them]]''. Six of them can be found on the [[Hermit Island]].\n\nThe Hermit Drying Rack works just like a [[Drying Rack/DST|Drying Rack]], except that it cannot be destroyed or burned and can only dry one item at a time.\n\n== Dryable Items ==\n{{#lsth:Drying Rack/DST|Dryable Items}}\n\n== [[File:Skins Icon.png|32px|link=]] Skins ==\n<noinclude>{{Main|Belongings#Natural Object Skins|Belongings}}</noinclude>\n* The '''<span class=\"skin-rarity-event\">Event</span>''' skin does not drop normally. Instead, it is usable by everyone during the official [[Winter's Feast]] event.\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;\">  \n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Coral Meat Rack Icon.png\n|rarity = Woven - Elegant\n|collection = Shelled Collection\n|name = Coral Meat Rack\n|description = Add a deliciously fishy kick to your jerky!\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Hermit_Drying_Rack_Merrymaker.png\n|rarity = Event\n|collection = The Merrymaker Collection\n|name =n/a\n|description =n/a\n}}\n</div>\n\n== [[File:Research Notes.png|32px|link=]] Assets == \n<tabber>\nHermit Drying Rack=\n<gallery>\nHermit Drying Rack.png|Build\nHermit Drying Rack Idle.gif|Idle\nHermit Drying Rack Burnt.png|Burnt (Unused)\n</gallery>\n|-|\nThe Merrymaker=\n<gallery>\nHermit Drying Rack Merrymaker.png|Build\nHermit Drying Rack Merrymaker Idle.gif|Idle\n</gallery>\n|-|\nCoral Meat Rack=\n<gallery>\nCoral Meat Rack Build.png|Build\nCoral Meat Rack Idle.gif|Idle\n</gallery>\n</tabber>\n\n=={{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nRWP WF25 Slots Concept Art.png|UI Slots concept art from ''Rhymes with Play'' stream.\nFile:Hermit Drying Rack UI Old.png|Hermit Drying Rack Old UI.\n</gallery>\n\n{{Structures}}\n[[vi:Hermit Drying Rack]]"
